Commercial Support

tmda-cgi has a free support infastructure including documentation, TMDA's public mailing lists, and searchable mailing list archives. These services are supported by the spare time of other tmda-cgi users.

If these resources aren't able to satisfy your needs, and you are willing to pay for additional help, we recommend you contact the program's author directly.

Gre7g will be glad to help your organization make TMDA accessible by users with limited computer knowledge and/or access.
